opinion: The best I had in LA
They did not offer sides of waffles with their entrees
perfect for a breezy Cali night
They have a unique twist on some common food items
Gotta try the Bloody Maria, classic
They also allow small dogs in the outdoor area
trying to do too much on their menu, so everything suffers a little
Feels like the Alcoves little cousin
A little too pretentious LA for my taste
